{"type": "article", "id": 23196, "title": "手提式边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-03T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110534ZhrQYT4Uz8nRXWsG.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是瑞典设计师 Alexander Lervik 在斯德哥尔摩家具展上展出的金属边桌，由一个圆弧框架和两个圆桌面组成，简单轻盈。上面的桌面可旋转 90 度，圆弧框架则充当了手提杆，因而也很方便提着它到处移动或者挂到墙边。具有北欧家具简洁优雅的特征。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110532dz2EJgp8IOmy6Wn0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.64850427\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110533GZw7E3Fl0kVJ9vqN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110533VHeIhYEoa9BpurNq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021105337AP1kByKqbEeltaI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7542735\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}